index.html: This file contains the main logic for the application, including the setup of the server and routing.
asset: This directory contains static assets such as images, stylesheets, and JavaScript files that are served to the client.
main.js: This file is the entry point for the application, initializing the server and defining the main routes.
style.css: This file contains the styles for the application, defining the look and feel of the user interface.
animations: This directory contains CSS animations that enhance the user experience by providing visual feedback and transitions.
